block content

    section(id='nc-groups' title='NC Groups')

        h1 NC Anthro Groups

        div(class='row row-cols-1 row-cols-xl-2')

            div(class='col mb-4')
                div(class='card h-100')
                    div(class='card-header') Western North Carolina Furs
                    div(class='card-body')
                        p(class='card-text')
                            | The Western North Carolina Furs are located in and around Asheville, NC. They try to have
                            | a fun activity planned at least once a month!
                    div(class='container')
                        div(class='row row-cols-2 row-cols-md-4')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='https://www.facebook.com/groups/WNCFurs/')
                                    i(class='fab fa-3x fa-facebook' title='Facebook Group')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='https://twitter.com/WNCFurs')
                                    i(class='fab fa-3x fa-twitter' title='Twitter')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='https://t.me/wncfurs')
                                    i(class='fab fa-3x fa-telegram' title='Telegram Chat')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='http://wncfurs2.com/')
                                    i(class='fas fa-3x fa-link' title='Link')

            div(class='col mb-4')
                div(class='card h-100')
                    div(class='card-header') Triad furs
                    div(class='card-body')
                        p(class='card-text')
                            | The Triad Furs is a group which holds regular furry meets in Greensboro, Winston-Salem, Highpoint
                            | and surrounding communities. They try to hold at least one group activity every month, on the third 
                            | Saturday, and they setup several dinner meets a month on weekday evenings.
                    div(class='container')
                        div(class='row')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='https://www.meetup.com/Greensboro-Furmeets-Meetup/')
                                    i(class='fas fa-3x fa-link' title='Website/Meetup')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='https://t.me/TriadFurs')
                                    i(class='fab fa-3x fa-telegram' title='Telegram Chat')
                            div(class='col text-center mb-4')
                                a(class='icon-link', href='https://twitter.com/TriadFurs')
                                    i(class='fab fa-3x fa-twitter' title='Twitter')

